Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
analyze_thermal(25.10)                                  analyze_thermal(25.10)

Name
       analyze_thermal  -  Specifies  to  invoke Celsius Thermal Solver to run
       die-only thermal analysis

Syntax
       analyze_thermal

       -help

       Specifies to invoke Celsius Thermal  Solver  to  run  die-only  thermal
       analysis.  The  command  generates the die temperature map file that is
       used by Voltus to run temperature-aware  power/IR/EM  analysis.  Before
       specifying  this  command, use the set_thermal_analysis_mode command to
       set the parameters for performing chip-centric thermal analysis.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs the command usage and a brief description about the com-
              mand parameters.

Examples
              * The following command specifies to run die-only thermal analy-
                sis:

                analyze_thermal

Related Information
              * set_thermal_analysis_mode

